interface chemistry 中文翻譯
中文翻譯手機版界面化學interface:    n. 分界面，兩個獨立體系的相交處。 vt. (-fac ...chemistry:    n. 1.化學。 2.物質的組成和化學性質；化學作用[現 ...colloid and interface chemistry:    膠體與界面化學chemistry:    n. 1.化學。 2.物質的組成和化學性質；化學作用[現象]。 3.〔比喻〕神秘的變化(過程)。  medical chemistry 藥物學。  ...as-interface:    不能使用濾波器; 模塊時if interface:    交接面interface:    n. 分界面，兩個獨立體系的相交處。 vt. (-faced, -facing) 把界面縫合。 vi. 交流，交談。 t-interface t:    接口colloid chemistry and physical chemistry:    物化膠化physical chemistry and colloid chemistry:    物化與膠化a textbook on chemistry:    化學課本acetylene chemistry:    乙炔化學agricultural chemistry:    農業化學air chemistry:    大氣化學amount of chemistry:    化學反應程度analysis chemistry:    分析化學analytic chemistry:    分析化學。 analytical chemistry:    分析化學; 教學經驗; 解析化學; 解析性化學animal chemistry:    動物化學applied chemistry:    應用化學。 aquatic chemistry:    水化學archaeological chemistry:    考古化學atmospheric chemistry:    大氣化學atom chemistry:    原子化學atomic chemistry:    原子化學
例句與用法The key laboratory of education ministry on colloid & interface chemistry was founded in 1993 at shandong university and has been formally opened to researchers at home and abroad since 1996山東大學膠體與界面化學教育部重點實驗室濟南市山大南路27號山東大學東校區郵編： 250100 Comprehensive studies on adsorption of ch4 , n2 , co2 single gas and their multicomponent gas on coal are conducted by applying physical chemistry , interface chemistry , coal petrology and coal chemical engineering knowledge本文運用物理化學、界面化學、煤巖學和煤化學等專業知識，較系統地研究了煤對氣體的吸附作用。對不同煤級煤吸附甲烷的特征及其變化規律進行了較詳細的分析。 Consequently concrete production practices are now being conducted by relying on more experiences or trial and error than related theory . so the study on the interfacial chemistry phenomena and rheological properties of the “ cement - water - superplasticizer ” system is in active demand . the systematical study on the interfacial properties and their influence factors based on the theory of colloidal science , interface chemistry , chemistry of cement and polymer science were conducted in order to establish the relationship among interfacial properties , microstructure and rheological characteristics of “ cement ? water - superplasticizer ” system , and provide the theoretical guide for the manufacture and applications of cement , concrete and superplasticizers本文選擇“水泥-水-高效減水劑”系統的界面化學現象和流變特征作為研究課題,旨在通過深入系統地研究水泥與高效減水劑在水介質中的一系列界面化學現象及其影響規律,利用膠體化學、界面化學、水泥化學和高分子化學的相關基礎理論,分析水泥與高效減水劑的相互作用機理,確定系統中界面化學現象、系統微觀結構和流變特性的關系,指導水泥、混凝土及外加劑的生產實踐。 用"interface chemistry"造句  


